Thelma and Louise star Susana Sarandon, 75, looks as though she hasn't aged a day following unearthed throwback snaps from her early acting career. Susan's peachy complexion and flame-haired tresses haven't changed a bit since her early acting days. The star shot to fame in the 1970 drama film Joe, before going on to star as Janet Weiss in The Rocky Horror Picture show. Her role as Louise in Thelma and Louise saw her nominated for an Academy Award for Best Actress, alongside multiple other film roles. The star's most recent work includes the upcoming TV drama, Monarch. Thelma and Louise is on tonight at 10.30p on BBC One.